    {
      "beat_id": "B02",
      "t_start": 5,
      "estimated_duration_s": 9,
      "narration_text": "Fire a ball at a wall higher than its energy. It reflects — kinetic energy converts to potential, runs out, reverses. The wall wins, always.",
