      "t_start": 79,
      "estimated_duration_s": 14,
      "narration_text": "In the scanning tunneling microscope, the tip hovers one nanometer above the surface. Moving it 0.1 nm closer multiplies the tunneling current by ten. That is how the STM images individual atoms.",
